# Common Compose Sequences | Regional Tags + Flag Emoji Rules
# [AUTHOR]: Carlos González Sanz
#
# > The purpose of this file is to store additional
# > Compose rules for typing regional & language tags
# > as well as flag emoji with the Compose Key (<Multi_key>).
#
# [Main sources]: 
# - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regional_indicator_symbol
# - https://emojipedia.org/es/banderas
#

# Color & Identity RGI Flags
#
# [Main source]: https://emojipedia.org/es/banderas
#
<Multi_key> <colon> <asterisk> <greater> <colon>        : "🏴"
<Multi_key> <colon> <bar> <asterisk> <greater> <colon>  : "🏁"
<Multi_key> <colon> <bar> <greater> <colon>             : "🚩"
<Multi_key> <colon> <greater> <colon>                   : "🏳️"


# Regional Tags
#
# [Main source]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tags_(Unicode_block)
#
<Multi_key> <period> <backspace> <period>   : "󠁿"    # Cancel tag (Allows finishing an emoji flag/tag sequence)
<Multi_key> <period> <less> <period>        : "󠁿"    # Cancel tag (Allows finishing an emoji flag/tag sequence)

##################
# [END OF RULES] #
